          <h3>Installing Unity components from the Unity package registry</h3>
          <p><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/get-npm">Install NPM</a> if you don't
            already have it on your system.</p>

          <p>Once NPM is installed, run the following command:
          <pre><code>
            npm adduser --registry https://registry.web.asu.edu
          </code></pre>
          <p>This will run you through a process to register a user on
          <a href="https://registry.web.asu.edu">https://registry.web.asu.edu</a></p>
          </p>

          <p>Now visit
            <a href="https://registry.web.asu.edu">https://registry.web.asu.edu</a> and
            login.
          </p>

          <p>Visit the page for the @asu-design-system package you wish to
            install. There you will find further instructions on how to
